high_descs: Turn right to reach the diningtable.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Turn around to reach the shelf and turn left to walk down the passage and turn left to enter the bathroom to reach the lemon in the sink.
Cut the lemon on the sink with the knife.
Put the knife on top of the sink.
Pick up a slice of lemon from the sink.
Turn right to walk down the passage and hang left to reach the microwave in the kitchen.
Heat the lemon slice in the microwave and take the lemon slice out.
Turn right to face the sink.
Put the lemon slice on the left sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated slice of Lemon on the left Sink.

high_descs: Go left to the diningtable.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Turn around, walk out of the exit in the upper left corner, and face the first entrance on your left, to a lemon bathroom.
Cut the lemon on the sink with the knife.
Place the knife on the sink.
Pick up a lemon slice from the sink.
Go right and then head left to an opening that you see there, with a sink and a microwave, and stand beside the sink just near the microwave.
Put the lemon slice in the microwave, heat the lemon up there for a while, then take the lemon out.
Take a step back then face the sink.
Put the lemon slice next to the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated-up Lemon next to the Sink

high_descs: walk to the diningtable that is next to two chairs.
pick up the knife from the table.
take the lemon to the sink in the other room.
Use the knife to cut the lemon that is on the sink.
Put the knife away in the sink.
pick up a lemon from the sink.
take the lemon in the microwave.
Put the lemon in the microwave and press start, then remove it.
Take the lemon to the sink.
Put the lemon on the tray next to the sink.
anns.task_desc: Get a lemon and bring it to the sink.
